    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Richmond Va</placeName>, <date>Jany 7<hi rend="sup"
                        >th</hi> 1857</date></p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <date>5617</date>
            </p>
            <p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>,</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>,</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">My Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">The Sunday School requires<lb/> the folly Books</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">1 doz <persName>Peixotto's</persName> Catechisms</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">1 “     <persName>Henry's</persName> Class Books,</p>
            <p>I should therefore feel obliged by your<lb/> forwarding them to me by Express,
                &amp;<lb/> am requested to state that should<lb/> you not have 1 doz
                    <persName>Henry's</persName> Class Books, you<lb/> will be good enough to send
                whatever less<lb/> you may have on hand.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">My Brother &amp; family desire their<lb/> kind regards to you, &amp;
                trusting you<lb/> are in the enjoyment of Health,</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I remain, my Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">Very Truly Yours</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <persName role="author">G<add>?</add> Jacob</persName>
            </p>
            <p>My Brother delivered a Lecture<lb/> before the Lit Society last
                <date>Sunday</date><lb/> afternoon, to a very large<lb/> auditory and with
                great<lb/> success—on “the Civilization<lb/> of the Ancients,” showing the<lb/>
                predominance of the Hebrew Race<lb/> over the there existing nations</p>
        </body>
